english.segment1: Tin man is what I'm called. Or puritan?. From the confederacy of my system. Defined relevance, from the immaculately attired
english.segment2: I am made from the wires, of my synthesizer. Made from the wires, made from the wires
english.segment3: Ideals from the pondering looks of eels. Written prescriptions by the ones who need them. My own feelings, shunned by group desires
